descriptionHtml:
"Missouri, Radio Scanners Police, Fire, EMS" app, live feeds from real scanners: police scanner, fire alarm, railroad radio, aircraft, emergency, news, and amateur radio.

Features:
- Police, Fire, EMS Radio feeds from Missouri - USA
- Save your favorite radio Stations
- Instant search
- Share with friends via Facebook, Twitter or Email
- Available horizontal and vertical orientation

descriptionHtml:
This app doesn’t represent a government entity.

This app does not belong to any government agency, to any government or organization, this app only collects free internet streams with the aim of informing. If you need accurate information of any kind, please contact your state or local authorities. This app is not intended to replace any official channel of information. This app is only for your personal use and the streams present in the app are freely available on the internet, the app only collects them by area to facilitate access to them.
